                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280529-251-off1383 t18280529-251-crimeloc1386"></join>. I missed a shawl and a pelisse from my bed-room, on the 3d of May - I suspected the prisoner, and found him on the 6th of May, in custody; I did not know him before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280529-251-person1356">
                  JOHN 
                  LAWS
               <interp inst="t18280529-251-person1356" type="surname" value="LAWS"></interp>
