                     <interp inst="t18280529-251-person1358" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker. On the 1st of May the prisoner pawned this pelisse, and on the 26th of April, this shawl.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. It was all through starvation.</p>
